properties.NAME: Rising Star Road
properties.DESC: Two lane road; surrounding land use is residential.
properties.JUST: Road connects a Minor Arterial and a Major Collector.  Also an indirect cut-through between SR 85 and SR 92.

properties.NAME: South Sandy Creek

properties.JUST: Connectivity between a Minor and Principal Arterial.  Increased in traffic from Pinewood Studios.  Serves Hospital and other non-residential developments.

properties.NAME: Flat Creek Trail
properties.DESC: Two lane road.
properties.JUST: North-south connectivity between a Principal Arterial and two minor arterials.

properties.NAME: Jenkins Road
properties.DESC: Two lane road.
properties.JUST: Serves school complex and cut-through between a Minor Arterial and SR 74.  Increase in traffic from Pinewood Studio development.

properties.NAME: Milam Road
properties.DESC: Two lane road.  Note - GIS segment includes both Milam Road and Rivers Road.  Both should be Minor Collectors (FC-6) but be independent road.

properties.NAME: Eastin/Graves Road
properties.DESC: Two lane road.

properties.DESC: Two lane road.

properties.NAME: Peters Road
properties.DESC: Two lane road.

properties.NAME: McElroy Road

properties.NAME: Hilo Raod
properties.DESC: Two lane road
properties.JUST: This road connects two Minor Arterials and serves as a collector for several large subdivisions.

properties.NAME: Kirkley Road
properties.DESC: Two lane road.  Note change is for entire segment between noted intersections.

properties.NAME: Castlewood Road
properties.DESC: Two lane road.
properties.JUST: Serves residential areas, Town of Tyrone, and indirect access to I-85 via Coweta County.  Proposed change should be consistent with similar changes on Coweta side of road.  Increasing traffic as congestion worsens on SR 74.

properties.NAME: Jenkins Road
properties.JUST: Serves school complex and cut-through between a Minor Arterial and SR 74.  Increase in traffic from Pinewood Studio development.
properties.DESC: Two lane road.  NOTE - combine the two Jenkins Road segments into one.  Section west of SR 74 can stay local.

properties.NAME: Bernhard Road

properties.NAME: Antioch Road
properties.DESC: Two-lane road, shoulder and ditch, feeds traffic to and from State Routes and City of Fayetteville.
properties.JUST: Antioch is classified as Major Collector north and south of this segment.

properties.NAME: McDonough Road
properties.DESC: Supports change # 556 in providing system continuity.
properties.JUST: Supports change # 556 in providing system continuity.

properties.NAME: Goza Road
properties.DESC: A two-lane, shoulder & ditch road.

properties.NAME: Hwy 85
properties.DESC: This change was proposed by GDOT.
properties.JUST: This change was proposed by GDOT.

properties.NAME: Banks Road
properties.DESC: Two-lane road, shoulder and ditch

properties.NAME: Kelly Road
properties.DESC: Varying number of lanes.

properties.NAME: Banks Road
